{"tid":1385403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【元朗示威4人涉藏武器提堂　不准保釋還押至9月再審】","createTime":"2019-07-30T05:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T08:34:33.000Z","uid":188721,"like":2,"dislike":98,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"8ec28da549d4d89fa1a0699d3be72e98e34c486a","tid":1385403,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:25:17.000Z","msg":"【元朗示威4人涉藏武器提堂　不准保釋還押至9月再審】<br />\n<br />\n上周六的光復元朗行動中，5名被捕男子今日（7月30日）提堂。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名23歲社工被控阻撓在正當執行職務的警務人員罪，其餘4名18至25歲男子各被控一項藏有攻擊性武器罪，5人今早於粉嶺裁判法院提訊。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官先將藏有武器案押後至9月3日再訊，以待繼續調查，涉藏有攻擊性武器的4名被告要還押候審。"},{"pid":"21375cf623f582a029f089f0c93f81e264030b4f","tid":1385403,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:28:44.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"63a47dda4380bbf21726534b253c7066f1283662","tid":1385403,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:28:54.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"947fe4ce3b4af2b1959dc1f3a58004898911d25f","tid":1385403,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:29:04.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"be16036060b16ba80bee57723ce1b13e82911a97","tid":1385403,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:29:26.000Z","msg":"救義士！"},{"pid":"22b7234597c49691f2454fa264fcaeada5361fbb","tid":1385403,"uid":58307,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"屌你老母,黑警死全家!"},{"pid":"7f33bb720b32f289b879682598d918b90d134669","tid":1385403,"uid":51050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:29:56.000Z","msg":"CLS"},{"pid":"3d82aaca1906a567264b33fb03f685ebbc4858ec","tid":1385403,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:29:57.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"936c70feea7f7fd5568174415c98733fdd117415","tid":1385403,"uid":188721,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/